# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# IMPORTANT NOTES FOR INVESTOR-SAFE USERS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# 1. START SMALL: Begin with paper trading or minimal capital ($50-100)
# 2. USE KRAKEN: Lowest fees are critical for conservative strategy
# 3. ENABLE COPY TRADING: Follow a proven master account
# 4. MONITOR WEEKLY: Check your account at least once per week
# 5. NEVER OVERRIDE: Do not disable safety features manually
# 6. BE PATIENT: Conservative trading requires patience
# 7. EXPECT FEWER TRADES: Quality over quantity (2-5 trades/week)
# 8. LOW RETURNS: Expect 2-5% monthly returns (conservative)
